<guid>https://picnob.com/post/6747232036626921581960</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[
Learning how to exercise my rights with the legend herself, @janefonda!If you didn’t already know, Jane Fonda has always been a badass, both on and off screen. She’s a longtime champion of free speech and the right to protest. I met her through the Committee for the First Amendment, which was originally formed during the McCarthy era by Hollywood heavyweights like her father, Henry Fonda. She relaunched it last year. Its mission to protect free speech against government repression and industry complicity has arguably never been more important, and I’m now a proud member of that committee.Thanks, Jane, for always standing up for our rights. And for squatting, lunging, stretching, and crunching for our rights too - haha. We filmed a workout skit today and I broke a sweat for real whereas Jane was as cool as a damn cucumber. Of course she was! @victorshi2020 @thegroundlings @1acommittee<p><img src="https://prank-arum.github.io/Feeds/Instagram/ellecordova/6747232036626921581960.jpg"><p><a href="https://picnob.com/post/6747232036626921581960">Original post on Picnob</a>]]>
</description>
<pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 18:04:41 -0400</pubDate>
